The sinners before you,
在你們面前的罪人

368
00:47:28,860 --> 00:47:32,870
sought to defend the heretic prince of Granada,
企圖保護格拉納達的異教王子

369
00:47:33,940 --> 00:47:40,160
the last heathen stronghold in our holy war.
那里是圣戰要攻下的最后一個異教徒據點

370
00:47:40,660 --> 00:47:42,550
So today,
所以今天

371
00:47:42,870 --> 00:47:47,110
before our king and queen
在國王和王后的見證下

372
00:47:47,330 --> 00:47:50,170
I swear we shall wash ourselves clean,
我發誓  我們都將在上帝的圣火中

373
00:47:50,170 --> 00:47:53,740
in the holy fire of God!
洗凈污穢

374
00:47:56,830 --> 00:47:58,670
Behold...
看啊

375
00:48:00,510 --> 00:48:02,830
God's will!
上帝的旨意

376
00:48:06,100 --> 00:48:07,460
You will watch your mentor burn
你將眼睜睜看著你的師父被燒死

377
00:48:07,750 --> 00:48:10,360
and then you will die the slowest.
然后你也將受盡折磨而死

378
00:48:25,200 --> 00:48:27,690
Give glory to the future.
將榮耀歸于未來

379
00:48:29,130 --> 00:48:31,450
Not to us.
而不是我們

380
00:49:07,660 --> 00:49:09,150
He is synchronizing.
他正在同步

381
00:49:24,890 --> 00:49:26,670
Damned heretics!
該死的異教徒

382
00:49:43,740 --> 00:49:45,490
Don't let them escape!
別讓他們跑了

383
00:55:19,540 --> 00:55:20,730
Jump.
跳啊

384
00:55:37,300 --> 00:55:39,000
Complete desynch.
解除同步完成

385
00:55:39,760 --> 00:55:41,160
Get him down!
放他下來

386
00:55:42,730 --> 00:55:44,510
Call the medics!
快叫醫護人員來

387
00:55:50,900 --> 00:55:55,020
Okay. It's okay. Cal, stay with me. Cal.
沒事了  卡爾  堅持住  卡爾

388
00:55:55,020 --> 00:55:57,690
Stay... It's okay. Hurry up!
堅持住  沒事了  快點

389
00:55:58,120 --> 00:56:01,500
Okay. Okay. Look at me.
沒事了  看著我

390
00:56:09,850 --> 00:56:11,210
Look at me.
看著我

391
00:56:36,240 --> 00:56:37,880
I can't feel my legs.
我的腿失去知覺了

392
00:56:38,840 --> 00:56:40,890
Paralysis is temporal.
身體麻痹只是暫時的

393
00:56:43,330 --> 00:56:45,330
What's the bad news?
壞消息是什么

394
00:56:45,330 --> 00:56:48,940
It caused a neurological split but we got you through it.
它引起了神經分裂  但我們把你治好了

395
00:56:49,450 --> 00:56:50,940
This time.
這一次僥幸而已

396
00:56:51,590 --> 00:56:53,860
I'm gonna die in here, aren't I?
我會死在這里的  對吧

397
00:56:57,550 --> 00:56:58,680
No.
不

398
00:57:00,800 --> 00:57:03,870
Not if you go in there on your own free will.
如果你憑借你的自由意志進去  就不會死

399
00:57:06,890 --> 00:57:08,810
I can't do this.
我做不到

400
00:57:09,730 --> 00:57:11,460
Yes, you can.
你可以的

401
00:57:11,730 --> 00:57:15,930
The Apple. You're the only one left who can find it.
能找到伊甸蘋果的人只剩下你了

402
00:57:16,650 --> 00:57:20,880
We can put an end to pain, Cal.
我們能結束痛苦  卡爾

403
00:57:21,890 --> 00:57:23,430
For everyone.
幫助所有人

404
00:57:51,560 --> 00:57:52,510
Where did you get this?
你從哪里找到的

405
00:57:52,510 --> 00:57:55,650
My father recovered it from the scene of your mother's murder.
我父親在你母親的兇殺現場找到的

406
00:57:55,650 --> 00:57:57,430
And brought it here for safekeeping.
然后帶到這里來保管

407
00:57:57,430 --> 00:57:59,390
Safekeeping?
保管

408
00:58:01,900 --> 00:58:02,950
You stole it.
你們這是偷竊

409
00:58:03,300 --> 00:58:06,020
It's your mother's necklace. I wanted you to have it.
這是你母親的項鏈  我想交給你

410
00:58:07,710 --> 00:58:08,850
Why was he there?
他為什么會去那里

411
00:58:09,230 --> 00:58:11,030
- To save her. - From whom?
-去救她  -誰要害她

412
00:58:11,170 --> 00:58:14,150
- Her own people. - What's that got to do with you?
-她的同僚  -那跟你有什么關系

413
00:58:14,750 --> 00:58:18,410
Assassins and Templars have been at war for centuries.
刺客和圣殿騎士已經交戰了數個世紀

414
00:58:18,800 --> 00:58:20,810
I aim to change that.
我希望能改變這局面

415
00:58:20,810 --> 00:58:23,080
That's right, I forgot.
對哦  我忘了

416
00:58:23,080 --> 00:58:25,160
We're here to combat aggression.
我們的目的是根除暴力

417
00:58:27,780 --> 00:58:30,210
I don't think I like your methods.
我不喜歡你的方式

418
00:58:31,890 --> 00:58:33,770
I am a scientist.
我是一個科學家

419
00:58:34,270 --> 00:58:36,670
I'm here to be cured of violence.
我來這里是為了治好我暴力的一面

420
00:58:38,400 --> 00:58:40,720
Who's gonna cure you?
但有誰能治好你呢

421
00:59:27,490 --> 00:59:29,450
We're feeding the beast.
我們是在喂養一頭野獸

422
00:59:30,660 --> 00:59:32,530
We're making him stronger.
我們在使他變得愈發強大

423
00:59:45,920 --> 00:59:47,760
I am Dr Rikkin.
我是萊肯博士

424
00:59:49,970 --> 00:59:51,500
Alan.
叫我亞倫吧

425
00:59:52,800 --> 00:59:55,900
I look after things here in Abstergo.
我負責管理阿布斯泰戈

426
00:59:58,180 --> 01:00:00,860
You like to keep things in the family, huh?
你不喜歡讓外人插手  對吧

427
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:02,270
Yes.
沒錯

428
01:00:03,770 --> 01:00:07,010
I'm sorry if we caused you any discomfort.
如果我們給你造成不適  很抱歉

429
01:00:07,610 --> 01:00:08,940
Is there anything I can do?
有什么需要我幫忙的嗎

430
01:00:08,940 --> 01:00:10,780
How about you let me out of here?
讓我離開這里怎么樣

431
01:00:20,500 --> 01:00:23,690
That's something I can't manage.
這件事我辦不到

432
01:00:26,380 --> 01:00:28,260
I'm here to make a deal.
我是來跟你做一筆交易的

433
01:00:30,090 --> 01:00:31,900
We need the Apple.
我們需要伊甸蘋果

434
01:00:33,680 --> 01:00:36,030
And we need you to get it for us.
也需要你幫我們找到它

435
01:00:37,560 --> 01:00:41,290
You've been desynching in the Animus.
你在阿尼姆斯里一直在解除同步

436
01:00:42,520 --> 01:00:44,730
We need you not to do that.
請你不要再那樣做

437
01:00:44,730 --> 01:00:47,010
Sending me back to the machine?
又要把我送進那臺機器里了嗎

438
01:00:47,730 --> 01:00:51,070
No, you've already shown us what we needed to see.
不  你已經讓我們看到我們需要看到的情形了

439
01:00:51,070 --> 01:00:52,810
Will you let us free then?
那你會釋放我們嗎

440
01:01:02,250 --> 01:01:04,770
What do you hope to gain from the newcomer?
你希望從那個新人身上得到什么

441
01:01:07,340 --> 01:01:09,660
Something that'll benefit us all.
能讓所有人都受益的東西

442
01:01:12,090 --> 01:01:13,850
You too, Moussa.
包括你  穆薩

443
01:01:38,910 --> 01:01:40,520
What have you done to them?
你對他們做了什么

444
01:01:42,120 --> 01:01:43,100
It's what happens
如果你用自己的意志

445
01:01:43,100 --> 01:01:47,440
if you don't enter in regression on your own volition.
進行時空回溯  就會產生這種后果

446
01:01:54,130 --> 01:01:55,480
Do you recognize this?
你認識這個嗎

447
01:01:56,970 --> 01:01:58,840
It's Assassin's blade.
這是刺客之刃

448
01:02:02,140 --> 01:02:04,460
This is the actual one...
你父親正是用這把刀

449
01:02:06,230 --> 01:02:09,630
your father used to take your mother's life.
奪去了你母親的生命

450
01:02:12,280 --> 01:02:13,950
He's here, you know?
他也在這里  你知道嗎

451
01:02:21,200 --> 01:02:23,360
Mother's death, Cal.
一個母親的死亡  卡爾

452
01:02:24,580 --> 01:02:27,570
Not something a boy should ever be made to see.
永遠不該讓她兒子看到

453
01:03:16,760 --> 01:03:18,270
This is wrong.
這樣做不對

454
01:03:18,760 --> 01:03:20,510
You left me no choice.
是你讓我別無選擇

455
01:03:20,510 --> 01:03:23,550
He has to go in on his own free will, you said that.
他一定要靠自己的自由意志進去  是你說的

456
01:03:23,550 --> 01:03:26,910
- I had to negotiate. - You mean manipulate?
-我只能去協商  -你是指操縱吧

457
01:03:28,930 --> 01:03:32,840
I assured the Elders we would have the Apple for London.
我向長老們承諾了我們會把伊甸蘋果送到倫敦

458
01:03:36,320 --> 01:03:37,980
That's in two days.
只剩下兩天時間了

459
01:03:40,280 --> 01:03:43,830
He doesn't want to know his past, or his father.
他不想知道自己的過去  也不想認識自己的父親

460
01:03:43,830 --> 01:03:46,770
He wants to destroy them, both.
他想毀掉這兩樣東西

461
01:03:47,000 --> 01:03:50,620
We're not in the business of creating monsters.
我們不是在制造怪物

462
01:03:50,620 --> 01:03:52,400
We neither created them nor destroyed them.
我們沒有制造它們  也沒有毀掉它們

463
01:03:52,400 --> 01:03:56,620
We merely abandoned them to their own inexorable faith.
我們不過是將它們拋向自己必然的信念

464
01:04:11,480 --> 01:04:15,430
- You're your mother's son. - What does that mean?
-你是你母親的孩子  -什么意思

465
01:04:18,650 --> 01:04:21,350
Blood that flows through you is not your own.
你體內的血液不屬于你自己

466
01:04:22,030 --> 01:04:24,020
Belongs to the Creed.
而屬于信條

467
01:04:24,700 --> 01:04:26,240
Your mother knew that.
你母親深知這一點

468
01:04:27,790 --> 01:04:30,110
She died so the Creed may live.
她用死換來信條的傳承

469
01:04:31,920 --> 01:04:35,030
Remind me how, exactly!
告訴我到底是怎么回事

470
01:04:37,130 --> 01:04:40,530
What you saw, I did.
你看到的事  是我干的

471
01:04:42,300 --> 01:04:43,980
You murdered her.
你殺了她

472
01:04:48,600 --> 01:04:52,260
I took her life rather than have it stolen by that machine.
我殺了她  總比讓那臺機器弄死她要好

473
01:04:54,940 --> 01:04:58,090
Man grows with the greatness of his task.
人因其崇高的使命而成長

474
01:04:59,780 --> 01:05:01,570
I ought to have killed you.
我應該把你也殺了

475
01:05:04,320 --> 01:05:05,770
I couldn't.
我下不了手

476
01:05:07,620 --> 01:05:09,090
Well, here.
給你

477
01:05:10,580 --> 01:05:11,820
Take it.
拿著

478
01:05:12,460 --> 01:05:15,000
Do what you couldn't do 30 years ago.
完成你30年前沒能做到的事

479
01:05:15,000 --> 01:05:17,320
It's in your hands now, Cal.
如今刺客之刃已在你手中  卡爾

480
01:05:18,130 --> 01:05:19,730
This is what they want.
這正是他們想要的結果

481
01:05:20,710 --> 01:05:22,700
Spill my blood.
殺了我

482
01:05:24,220 --> 01:05:26,870
But do not go back in the Animus.
但千萬不要再進入阿尼姆斯

483
01:05:27,210 --> 01:05:28,480
Why?
為什么

484
01:05:29,730 --> 01:05:34,420
The Apple contains the genetic code for free will.
伊甸蘋果當中蘊含著自由意志的基因密碼

485
01:05:34,780 --> 01:05:36,970
