他們會用來毀滅我們

486
01:05:38,870 --> 01:05:40,390
I'm gonna find it.
我一定會找到的

487
01:05:42,750 --> 01:05:47,280
And watch them destroy you and your Creed.
然后看著他們  毀掉你和你的信條

488
01:05:48,200 --> 01:05:50,470
You can not kill the Creed.
信條是殺不死的

489
01:05:50,700 --> 01:05:52,380
It's in your blood.
它根植于你的血液中

490
01:05:53,080 --> 01:05:55,400
The Apple is everything.
伊甸蘋果就是一切

491
01:05:55,790 --> 01:05:58,110
Your mother died to protect it.
你母親為了保護它犧牲了生命

492
01:06:01,130 --> 01:06:03,450
She had no choice.
她當年別無選擇

493
01:06:11,970 --> 01:06:13,460
I do.
但我有

494
01:07:00,050 --> 01:07:01,960
You're gonna kill the Creed!
你要殺了信條

495
01:07:09,940 --> 01:07:11,660
Take me to the Animus.
帶我去阿尼姆斯

496
01:07:20,120 --> 01:07:21,420
Put me in.
把我放進去

497
01:07:22,250 --> 01:07:24,030
Prepare the Animus.
準備阿尼姆斯

498
01:07:23,960 --> 01:07:25,750
Voluntary regression.
自愿回溯

499
01:07:28,920 --> 01:07:31,740
Do you know how the Assassins came to be named?
你知道殺手的名字是怎么得來的

500
01:07:32,260 --> 01:07:36,320
From an Arabic word "Hashashin".
是根據阿拉伯詞語"哈薩辛"演變來的

501
01:07:36,760 --> 01:07:38,790
They were society's outcasts.
他們曾是社會的棄徒

502
01:07:38,790 --> 01:07:42,880
Those who stole, who murdered in cold blood.
他們會偷盜  冷血地殺人

503
01:07:44,270 --> 01:07:48,940
People ridiculed them... Rebels, fools, drug addicts.
人們都嘲弄他們  叛黨  白癡  癮君子

504
01:07:48,940 --> 01:07:51,220
But they were wise.
但其實他們很明智

505
01:07:51,820 --> 01:07:55,900
They used this reputation to hide the dedication to principles
他們利用這種罵名  來隱藏自身對信條的忠貞

506
01:07:55,900 --> 01:07:58,930
beyond those of even their strongest enemies.
甚至瞞過了最強大的敵人

507
01:07:59,370 --> 01:08:04,330
And for that I admire them.
為此  我很欽佩他們

508
01:08:07,960 --> 01:08:10,220
But you're not one of those men.
但你不是其中的一員

509
01:08:11,170 --> 01:08:12,640
Are you?
對吧

510
01:08:13,930 --> 01:08:15,410
Let's find out.
那就試試看吧

511
01:08:23,480 --> 01:08:25,180
Commencing regression.
開始回溯

512
01:08:31,750 --> 01:08:33,690
This is my life's work.
這是我畢生的事業

513
01:08:35,570 --> 01:08:37,290
It's my life.
這是我的生命

514
01:09:25,500 --> 01:09:27,130
For the Creed.
為了信條

515
01:09:31,240 --> 01:09:33,290
Our own lives...
我們自身的生命

516
01:09:33,710 --> 01:09:36,950
What matters is what we leave behind.
重要的是  我們為后世留下什么

517
01:09:53,610 --> 01:09:55,030
Sultan...
蘇丹

518
01:09:56,240 --> 01:09:57,830
Surrender the Apple.
把伊甸蘋果交出來

519
01:09:58,000 --> 01:10:00,680
Your Assassin protectors are gone.
那些保護你的刺客都已經走了

520
01:10:01,120 --> 01:10:04,650
The Creed is finished.
信條已經完了

521
01:10:45,160 --> 01:10:46,670
My son.
我兒

522
01:11:25,910 --> 01:11:31,110
Here lies the seed of man's first disobedience,
這里面是人類第一次違抗命令的種子

523
01:11:32,790 --> 01:11:34,920
of free will itself.
是自由意志

524
01:11:45,090 --> 01:11:47,870
Thanks to the Apple of Eden,
多虧了伊甸蘋果

525
01:11:48,220 --> 01:11:50,540
the known world
這已知的世界

526
01:11:51,180 --> 01:11:53,880
shall be ushered into a new age.
將會被引入新紀元

527
01:11:54,690 --> 01:11:57,010
One of peace,
一個和平的新紀元

528
01:11:57,400 --> 01:12:01,030
in which all the warring populations of mankind
在那里  所有彼此敵對的人類

529
01:12:01,030 --> 01:12:07,890
shall bow in perfect obedience to our one templar rule.
將完全服從圣殿的統治

530
01:13:13,060 --> 01:13:15,100
The Apple.
伊甸蘋果

531
01:13:15,810 --> 01:13:17,280
Give it to him.
交給他

532
01:13:18,690 --> 01:13:20,080
Now.
立刻

533
01:13:23,230 --> 01:13:24,850
For the Creed.
為了信條

534
01:15:26,360 --> 01:15:27,440
Go!
快走

535
01:16:29,500 --> 01:16:30,890
Forgive me.
原諒我

536
01:18:08,600 --> 01:18:09,990
It's over!
已經結束了

537
01:18:15,820 --> 01:18:17,880
Assassin!
有刺客

538
01:18:46,560 --> 01:18:48,470
A leap of faith.
信仰之躍

539
01:19:11,830 --> 01:19:13,120
Where are we?
現在在哪兒

540
01:19:15,090 --> 01:19:17,130
It looks like a military port.
似乎是個軍事港口

541
